title: Rough Waves
body:
read it on the AO3 at http://bit.ly/2GdXjXW

by EnviousHera

Inspired heavily by R. L. Stine’s Beach House.

1991: Jyn Erso and her friends are vacationing in the beautiful beach town of Tattooine with their families, when they make friends with the strange and intense Ben Solo. Jyn falls hard.

2019: Rey and her best friend (and kind of boyfriend) Finn are visiting Tattooine the summer after graduation when they make friends with the rich and dashing Kylo Ren. Both are confused by their feelings towards him (and each other) as Kylo plays both sides for fun.

Both summers quickly turn into a horror story, spanning decades. But what’s the connection? And what is up with the creepy beach house on the shore?
